li.p: Measured in continuous TX or RX mode with core 0 idle at 4 MHz and peripherals disabled.
Advertising in three channels using the Low-Power Advertising (LOWPAD) application and TX packet length of 27 bytes.
The flash is supplied by VDDIO and, when idle, consumes a small amount of DC current.
